\c 18
\p
\v 1 Haiwa, nyika inovirira mapapiro, iri mhiri kwenzizi dzeItiyopiya,
\v 2 inotuma nhume ne\add nzira dze\add*gungwa, nemagwa enhokwe pamusoro pemvura! Endai, nhume dzinokurumidza, muende kurudzi rwakareba uye rwunotsvedzerera paganda, kurudzi rwunotyisa, kubva apo zvichienda mberi, rudzi rwune simba rwunotsika-tsika pasi, rune nyika inokamurwa nenzizi.
\v 3 Imwi mese vagari vepanyika, nemwi mugere panyika, tarirai panosimudzwa mureza pamakomo; inzwai panoridzwa hwamanda!
\v 4 Nokuti Jehovha wakareva aizvozvoseizvi kwandiri: Ndichanyarara, ndichatarira ndiri paugaro hwangu, semurazvo wemushana unopisa, segore redova pakupisa kwe\add nguva ye\add*kukohwa.
\v 5 Nokuti kukohwa kusati kwavapo, ruva rakwana, uye chibereko chemuzambiringa usina kuibva chinoibva \add shure\add* kwemaruva, zvino achagura matavi nemapanga ekuchekerera, abvise matavi, amateme.
\v 6 Zvichasiiwa pamwe zvive zveshiri dzemakomo, nezvemhuka dzepanyika, uye magora achapedza chirimo pamusoro pazvo, nemhuka dzese dzepanyika dzichapedzera chando pamusoro pazvo.
\p
\v 7 Nenguva iyo kuchaunzwa chipo kuna Jehovha wehondo, kurudzi rwakareba uye rwunotsvedzerera paganda, kurudzi rwunotyisa, kubva apo zvichienda mberi, rudzi rwune simba rwunotsika-tsika pasi, rune nyika inokamurwa nenzizi, chiende kunzvimbo yezita raJehovha wehondo, gomo reZiyoni.